      "id": "1826992588599358",
      "title": "Slay the Spire 2's daily runs have turned me into a spoiled brat",
      "link": "https://steamstore-a.akamaihd.net/news/externalpost/PCGamesN/1826992588599358",
      "pubDate": "Sun, 15 Mar 2026 09:00:20 GMT",
      "publishedAt": "2026-03-15T09:00:20.000Z",
      "kind": "news",
      "category": "news",
      "sourceLabel": "PCGamesN",
      "author": "editor@pcgamesn.com",
      "official": false,
      "external": true,
      "image": "https://www.pcgamesn.com/wp-content/sites/pcgamesn/2026/03/slay-the-spire-2-daily-runs-have-spoiled-me-overpowered-combo-decks-modifiers-infinite-relics-sts2-mega-crit-900x506.jpg",
      "summary": "The Slay the Spire 2 daily has ruined me. I'm usually such a good boy. I read tutorials. I study tooltips and glossaries to ensure I understand every keyword. I carefully calculate my turns to ensure I'm getting the most juice out of every card I squeeze. Unfortunately, after a week of gorging myself on the delicious combos and ultra-sleek loadouts that Mega Crit's challenge mode has to offer, I've become a monster, petulantly banging my fists on the digital table and whining to mommy Neow that I don't want any Strikes and Defends in my deck.\nRead the rest of the story...\nRELATED LINKS:\nNew medieval game Kinstrife, built by Mount and Blade modders, wants you to \"truly lose yourself in the fantasy\"\nManor Lords makes families matter more as housing gets a new upgrade\nFreak Steam game naming coincidence unintentionally results in some of the best indie marketing I've seen",
      "summaryKo": "The Slay the Spire 2 daily has ruined me. I'm usually such a good boy. I read tutorials. I study tooltips and glossaries to ensure I understand every keyword. I carefully calculate my turns to ensure I'm getting the most juice out of every card I squeeze. Unfortunately, after a week of gorging myself on the delicious combos and ultra-sleek loadouts that Mega Crit's challenge mode has to offer, I've become a monster, petulantly banging my fists on the digital table and whining to mommy Neow that I don't want any Strikes and Defends in my deck.",
